vc_row][vc_row el_class=\"hh\"][vc_column][vc_row_inner][vc_column_inner width=\"1/4\"][icon_box border=\"0\" title=\"Calidad\" image=\"217\"]Servicios diferenciados y de alto valor.[/icon_box][/vc_column_inner][vc_column_inner width=\"1/4\"][icon_box border=\"0\" title=\"Eficacia\" image=\"223\"]Aportan soluciones reales y útiles.[/icon_box][/vc_column_inner][vc_column_inner width=\"1/4\"][icon_box border=\"0\" title=\"Confianza\" image=\"226\"]Servicio personalizado y flexible que genera confianza.[/icon_box][/vc_column_inner][vc_column_inner width=\"1/4\"][icon_box border=\"0\" title=\"Profesionalismo\" image=\"229\"]Ética, Pasión, Confidencialidad y Transparencia[/icon_box][/vc_column_inner][/vc_row_inner][/vc_column][/vc_row][vc_row full_width=\"stretch_row_content_no_spaces\" equal_height=\"yes\" content_placement=\"middle\" css=\".vc_custom_1601423784339{background-color: #eeeeee !important;}\"][vc_column width=\"1/2\"][vc_video][/vc_column][vc_column width=\"1/2\"][vc_row_inner css=\".vc_custom_1601423858768{padding-right: 50px !important;padding-left: 50px !important;}\"][vc_column_inner][vc_column_text]\r\n<h3><strong>I am text block.</strong></h3>\r\nClick edit button to change this text. Lorem ipsum dolor sit amet, consectetur adipiscing elit. Ut elit tellus, luctus nec ullamcorper mattis, pulvinar dapibus leo.[/vc_column_text][vc_btn title=\"Brochure\" style=\"classic\" color=\"danger\" align=\"center\" i_icon_fontawesome=\"fa fa-bookmark-o\" button_block=\"true\" add_icon=\"true\"][/vc_column_inner][/vc_row_inner][/vc_column][/vc_row][vc_row content_placement=\"middle\" css=\".vc_custom_1601425099848{margin-top: 70px !important;margin-bottom: 35px !important;}\"][vc_column width=\"1/3\"][vc_custom_heading text=\"STAFF PROFESIONAL\" font_container=\"tag:h2|font_size:24px|text_align:left\" use_theme_fonts=\"yes\"][/vc_column][vc_column width=\"2/3\"][vc_column_text el_class=\"texto\"]Nuestro staff profesional es fundamental, nuestra Firma toma con  serie